quoteText: Our Site does not honor “do not track signals” (e.g., the Mozilla Firefox Do Not Track feature), though you may be able to disable certain tracking as discussed above (e.g., by disabling cookies).
title: This service ignores the Do Not Track (DNT) header and tracks users anyway even if they set this header.
